# No third-party chat / push embeds

- Do **not** paste PushEngage, Tawk.to, Tidio, HubSpot chat, Crisp, Chaty, LiveChat, or similar consumer chat / web-push scripts into NR2 SoftDent, optical, or financial pages.
- Visiting vendor marketing pages does not inject code into NR2; only installing embeds would.
- Keep HAL UI flash rings disabled (`hal-live-widget-bridge.js` `flashElement` no-op) unless the operator explicitly requests otherwise.
- Prefer on-workstation HAL / SoftDent read-only flows over third-party SaaS widgets (PHI / fiduciary surface).
